Description: 1994 PRS Paul Reed Smith Dragon III #71 The Dragon III combines a 438 piece Dragon Inlay of Gold,Red and Green Abalone, Mother of Pearl, Mammoth Ivory and Stone with our bestwoods. It features a select Mahogany back with a beautiful carved Maple top, 22Frets, the PRS Stop-tail, Original Dragon pickups, a Wide-Fat neck and Goldhardware. The Dragon III is a work of art and a joy to play. Very collectableinstrument. Dragon III Specs One-piece mahogany wide-fat set-neck, rosewood fingerboardwith third-style Dragon inlay 22 frets “Dragon III” ontruss-rod cover, gold inlaid signature on headstock, locking tuners Solid mahogany body,figured maple top Color option: darkcherry Two humbuckers(Dragon Treble & Bass) Volume, Tone,five-way rotary pickup switch PRS Stoptail * limited edition 71 of100 Serial: 4 19465 Comes with Original Leather Hardshell Case Prefer Guitar to be inspected locally.
